              <Comments>In {S:05800200700006} (a quotation from Psalm {D:8.6}) the expression βραχύ τι as a lexical unit refers to rank. However, {S:05800200800000} suggests that the writer of Hebrews probably interpreted βραχύ as meaning a small quantity (see {D:59.14}) and as referring to time in the sense of ‘a little (while).’ For this interpretation of τι, see {D:92.12}.</Comments>
